:parml compact tsize=12 break=fit.
:pt.:hp3.Purpose&colon.:ehp3.:pd.Draw a horizontal line on the screen.
.br
:pt.:hp3.Format&colon.:ehp3.:pd.:hp2.DRAWHLINE:ehp2. :hp3.row column len
style:ehp3. :hp2.[BRIght] [BLInk] fg ON [BRIght] bg:ehp2.
