:pt.:pd.:hp3.row :ehp3.&colon. Starting row
:pt.:pd.:hp3.column :ehp3.&colon. Starting column
:pt.:pd.:hp3.len :ehp3.&colon. Length of line
:pt.:pd.:hp3.style :ehp3.&colon. Line drawing style&colon.
.* FIX FIX FIX sub-indentation
:pt.:pd.    :hp2.1:ehp2.   Single line
:pt.:pd.    :hp2.2:ehp2.   Double line
:pt.:pd.:hp3.fg :ehp3.&colon. Foreground character color
:pt.:pd.:hp3.bg :ehp3.&colon. Background character color
