:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_ChangeTitle.ChangeTitle:elink.:pd.Session title changes
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_CMDDirMvCpy.CMDDirMvCpy:elink.:pd.Copy/Move a directory to the target instead of the files in the directory (same behavior as CMD)
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_CommandSep.CommandSep:elink.:pd.Multiple command separator character
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_CursorIns.CursorIns:elink.:pd.Cursor shape in insert mode
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_CursorOver.CursorOver:elink.:pd.Cursor shape in overstrike mode
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_DateFmt.DateFmt:elink.:pd.Date Format (e.g. YYYY-MM-DD)
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_DecimalChar.DecimalChar:elink.:pd.DecimalChar
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_DescriptionMax.DescriptionMax:elink.:pd.Maximum length of file descriptions
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_DescriptionName.DescriptionName:elink.:pd.Name of file to hold file descriptions
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_Descriptions.Descriptions:elink.:pd.Enable / disable description processing
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_EditMode.EditMode:elink.:pd.Editing mode (insert / overstrike)
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_EscapeChar.EscapeChar:elink.:pd.4OS2 escape character
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_EvalMax.EvalMax:elink.:pd.Max digits after decimal point in @EVAL
:pt.:link reftype=hd refid=INI_EvalMin.EvalMin:elink.:pd.Min digits after decimal point in @EVAL
